Subject: clk: rockchip: Add binding ids for cpu and peri clocks on rk3066
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 550a13315e3196b332dd05f970908c0babd0ce93
